00:39:34.179 --> 00:39:39.820
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Like you're you're not generally experiencing that, certainly at, you know, at camp.

821
00:39:39.820 --> 00:39:46.840
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Like I think the idea of going to a camp and there being multiple non-verbal is probably unlikely unless it's a specialised camp.

822
00:39:46.840 --> 00:39:48.579
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: I just thought it was nice.

823
00:39:47.500 --> 00:39:48.002
