00:39:58.679 --> 00:40:07.502
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Meanwhile, you're all trying to figure each other out and y'all have, you know, certain things you could do, certain limitations, and you still find a way to communicate with each other in the game, which is.

827
00:39:59.000 --> 00:39:59.502
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Mm-hmm.

828
00:40:07.000 --> 00:40:07.719
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Mm-hmm.

829
00:40:07.719 --> 00:40:09.039
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.

