00:40:46.480 --> 00:40:51.159
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: I strongly believe that when someone uses a communication board, they are they are talking.

843
00:40:51.639 --> 00:41:01.239
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Um, so you have the, you have your board and you start off with a few different symbols and then you, you gather more as you're doing.

844
00:40:52.000 --> 00:40:52.502
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Oh yeah.

845
00:41:01.239 --> 00:41:06.880
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: I think it's an interesting way to do things because I I mean, I guess suspension of disbelief for a minute.

