<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Well, exact- exactly.

850
00:41:18.159 --> 00:41:19.000
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: That's my point.

851
00:41:19.000 --> 00:41:21.699
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Suspension of disbelief, just just been now there.

852
00:41:21.699 --> 00:41:30.219
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: But I thought it was interesting where you gather symbols for places and things and people as you as you encounter them.

853
00:41:30.500 --> 00:41:31.219
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Yes.

854
00:41:30.940 --> 00:41:32.920
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: So it's like,

855
00:41:31.219 --> 00:41:34.002
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Yeah, you build on what you build on the start of it.

856
00:41:33.400 --> 00:41:34.900
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Exactly.

857
00:41:34.900 --> 00:41:44.739
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: So it's like you encounter a person and you ask who they are and they give you a symbol for who they are, which by the way, lovely thing is that these people were prepared for this.

858
00:41:44.739 --> 00:42:00.699
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: One thing that lots of people's experiences will be very different, but my experience with Nathan and his, so he goes to mainstream school one day a week and his class that he's grown up with now, he's 11 now.

859
00:41:50.000 --> 00:41:50.502
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Yes.

860
00:42:00.699 --> 00:42:05.559
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: They are like super inclusive of him.

861
00:42:05.559 --> 00:42:06.880
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: They're so kind to him.

862
00:42:06.880 --> 00:42:08.559
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: They will they will talk to him.

