866
00:42:21.880 --> 00:42:33.400
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: It's like, oh, people being so accepting of this person and how they communicate by being like, oh, yes, I'm so-and-so, here's a symbol that you can use to refer to me is just really nice.

867
00:42:33.000 --> 00:42:33.960
