00:42:37.559 --> 00:42:39.420
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Um.

871
00:42:39.719 --> 00:42:45.059
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: But, uh, no, that's great for, at school being included that way.

872
00:42:45.059 --> 00:42:55.139
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: And just personally, as for myself, like as a parent, yes, I experience outside, not to the degree that you have, but, um, my job, I'm a personal support worker.

