00:43:06.119 --> 00:43:15.599
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: I don't do sign language, but like I can understand a little bit of it and just seeing and you just communicate as you would, anyone else, or you try at least.

877
00:43:15.599 --> 00:43:26.002
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Um, yeah, I'm sorry, I lost my train of thought there, but yeah, no, it's, it's great to have anyone that they can, you know, try to feel like they're including somebody in this situation.

878
00:43:19.500 --> 00:43:20.002
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: No, no.

