00:43:36.039 --> 00:43:37.719
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: That is the entire game.

882
00:43:37.719 --> 00:43:44.559
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: I think it's a really interesting, so we talked a big at the beginning about making other people play the game.

