00:43:55.500 --> 00:44:11.340
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: That's what I was thinking too, because it's like, okay, so if I'm getting a little bit frustrated, try to think what symbol do I use in the situation, I think that's where you were going, imagine in real life, the situation of this is not exactly what I want to say, but I'm limited to these pictures and words on a board.

