<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: That is that is his his goalen life is to eat as much as possible.

1504
01:20:47.500 --> 01:20:48.502
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Okay.

1505
