01:20:53.439 --> 01:21:00.760
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Um, so we started off with that and um, and then it took his another couple of years to get to the 2nd symbol.

1507
01:20:53.500 --> 01:20:54.002
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Yeah.

