1510
01:21:04.500 --> 01:21:05.460
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Oh, it was huge.

1511
01:21:05.460 --> 01:21:06.899
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: It was absolutely huge.

1512
01:21:06.899 --> 01:21:10.619
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: The problem then is we tried a few different symbols that were for different things.

1513
01:21:10.619 --> 01:21:17.279
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: We tried using symbols to toilet training, for example, and it didn't go anywhere and then we tried a couple of other things.

1514
01:21:17.279 --> 01:21:26.520
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Eventually, um, we kind of just, we gave up on adding new symbols for ages and then maybe like a year and a half ago we started again.

1515
01:21:26.520 --> 01:21:43.020
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: And we added a few more symbols and we managed to get there because a while, but we got there with a couple more symbols and we're now at the point where he's actually managing to pick up on symbols with only a couple of weeks of work.

1516
01:21:33.000 --> 01:21:34.002
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Wow.

1517
01:21:41.500 --> 01:21:42.460
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Oh wow.

1518
01:21:43.020 --> 01:21:56.939
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: So we've, in fact, I got one today where he used it on his own without any prompting asking for something that he wanted for the 1st time for that symbol and that feeling is just amazing.

1519
01:21:57.500 --> 01:21:59.180
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Oh, wow, what was it?

