<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: It was bacon.

1521
01:22:02.000 --> 01:22:02.779
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Perfect.

1522
01:22:02.779 --> 01:22:04.159
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Yes that's a good motivator.

1523
01:22:04.420 --> 01:22:05.859
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: He loves bacon.

1524
01:22:05.859 --> 01:22:23.560
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Bacon is one of his things, but he, his, the way he used to ask for bacon was take you to the fridge, you'd open the fridge and then you'd tap the bacon, which like, in its way, is fine, but like we really, I think this is one of the reasons why we used bacon as one of these ones is because it's a very clear we know what he's asking for.

1525
01:22:13.000 --> 01:22:13.502
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Okay.

1526
01:22:23.560 --> 01:22:29.319
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: And then we go, okay, if you want bacon, you come here and you use this symbol, bacon, and then we do the bacon.

1527
01:22:29.319 --> 01:22:35.260
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: But today was the 1st day that the 1st time that he asked for bacon using the symbol without any other prompting.

1528
01:22:35.260 --> 01:22:36.340
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Like he just, he took me.

1529
01:22:35.500 --> 01:22:36.502
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Oh, wow.

1530
01:22:36.340 --> 01:22:40.720
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: He took me to his communication device and I said, yeah, what can I do for you?

1531
01:22:40.720 --> 01:22:48.279
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: And he looked at me and he looked at the tablet and he tapped bacon and he looked back at me and I said, yes, you can have bacon and he bounced.

1532
01:22:48.279 --> 01:22:52.779
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: He was so happy because I think he.

1533
01:22:50.000 --> 01:22:52.819
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Out of any time in your life, you can have bacon now.

1534
01:22:52.779 --> 01:22:56.500
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Well, this is the... This is the thing.

1535
01:22:52.819 --> 01:22:54.859
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: This is a time you're going to be getting your baking.

1536
01:22:56.500 --> 01:23:02.140
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: We've actually, we've actually talked about like if he ever does use, say a word out loud using his voice.

1537
01:23:02.140 --> 01:23:08.140
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: I think no matter what word that is, if he's asking for something, he's getting it.

1538
01:23:08.140 --> 01:23:09.819
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Right?

1539
01:23:09.500 --> 01:23:10.340
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Of course.

1540
01:23:09.819 --> 01:23:11.619
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Like, literally whatever it is.

1541
01:23:10.340 --> 01:23:11.539
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Oh my gosh.

1542
01:23:11.539 --> 01:23:12.002
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Yeah.

1543
01:23:11.619 --> 01:23:12.760
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: You know, you know what?

1544
01:23:12.760 --> 01:23:15.159
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: At this point, I'd be happy if his 1st word was a swear word.

1545
01:23:15.279 --> 01:23:16.720
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Right?

1546
01:23:16.500 --> 01:23:18.180
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Yes.

1547
01:23:16.720 --> 01:23:19.779
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Like I just, I, you know, it's, it's one of these things.

1548
01:23:19.779 --> 01:23:23.439
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: So yeah, it was amazing for him to ask for that.

1549
01:23:23.439 --> 01:23:26.800
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: And I think he felt that as well with how excited he was.

1550
