<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Maybe he was just excited for the bacon.

1551
01:23:27.500 --> 01:23:29.502
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: Oh. Well.

1552
01:23:28.539 --> 01:23:31.899
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Maybe he was excited because he'd managed to use a new one.

1553
01:23:31.899 --> 01:23:32.380
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: I don't know.

1554
01:23:33.000 --> 01:23:34.319
<v 75AE8ACE-FE15-4280-8B00-188C37215357>Chelsea: No, that's huge though.

1555
