<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Most of them are, I think some of them are, some of them are really great.

1567
01:24:21.300 --> 01:24:24.720
<v AF2CBEBB-3493-475E-82E9-7A7A0C03AAF3>Al: Some of them are trying but overstretched.

